metadata.name: Wiggle #1
metadata.description:
World of Wiggles is a collection of 5555 randomly generated and unique NFT art pieces created by our visual artist team. The collection represents women from around the world and the traits go beyond the diversity of just skin colors. Our goal it  to make the world a better place!
World of Wiggles allows art lovers to own a unique art piece while also making the NFT space more diverse and inclusive.
Join us in our journey as we try to lift up and help bring Women led projects to the forefront of NFT space!
